### Test Approval Endpoints
### Make sure the backend server is running on localhost:8080

### 1. Health Check
GET http://localhost:8080/health

### 2. Login as Requester (Get JWT Token)
POST http://localhost:8080/api/v1/auth/login
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "email": "requester@demo.com",
  "password": "password"
}

### 3. Get Requisitions (should show our test data)
GET http://localhost:8080/api/v1/requisitions
Authorization: Bearer YOUR_JWT_TOKEN_HERE
Content-Type: application/json

### 4. Get Specific Requisition by Number (REQ-001) - WORKING ✅
GET http://localhost:8080/api/v1/requisitions/REQ-001
Authorization: Bearer YOUR_JWT_TOKEN_HERE
Content-Type: application/json

### 5. Get Specific Requisition by Number (REQ-002) - WORKING ✅
GET http://localhost:8080/api/v1/requisitions/REQ-002
Authorization: Bearer YOUR_JWT_TOKEN_HERE
Content-Type: application/json

### 6. Get Specific Requisition by UUID - WORKING ✅
GET http://localhost:8080/api/v1/requisitions/b4a042e8-0b62-488e-995a-7233c46b4c5f
Authorization: Bearer YOUR_JWT_TOKEN_HERE
Content-Type: application/json

### 7. Get Approval History for REQ-001
GET http://localhost:8080/api/v1/documents/REQ-001/approval-history
Authorization: Bearer YOUR_JWT_TOKEN_HERE
Content-Type: application/json

### 8. Get Approval Status for REQ-001 - WORKING ✅
GET http://localhost:8080/api/v1/documents/REQ-001/approval-status
Authorization: Bearer YOUR_JWT_TOKEN_HERE
Content-Type: application/json

### 9. Get Approval Status for REQ-002 (should show pending finance approval) - WORKING ✅
GET http://localhost:8080/api/v1/documents/REQ-002/approval-status
Authorization: Bearer YOUR_JWT_TOKEN_HERE
Content-Type: application/json

### 10. Get Available Approvers for Requisitions - WORKING ✅
GET http://localhost:8080/api/v1/approvals/available-approvers?documentType=REQUISITION
Authorization: Bearer YOUR_JWT_TOKEN_HERE
Content-Type: application/json

### 11. Get Available Approvers for Stage 1 - WORKING ✅
GET http://localhost:8080/api/v1/approvals/available-approvers?documentType=REQUISITION&stage=1
Authorization: Bearer YOUR_JWT_TOKEN_HERE
Content-Type: application/json

### 12. Get Approval Tasks (should show pending tasks)
GET http://localhost:8080/api/v1/approvals
Authorization: Bearer YOUR_JWT_TOKEN_HERE
Content-Type: application/json

### 13. Get Approval Tasks assigned to me
GET http://localhost:8080/api/v1/approvals?assigned_to_me=true
Authorization: Bearer YOUR_JWT_TOKEN_HERE
Content-Type: application/json

### 14. Get Pending Approval Tasks
GET http://localhost:8080/api/v1/approvals?status=pending
Authorization: Bearer YOUR_JWT_TOKEN_HERE
Content-Type: application/json

### 15. Get Specific Approval Task (replace TASK_ID with actual task ID from step 12)
GET http://localhost:8080/api/v1/approvals/TASK_ID
Authorization: Bearer YOUR_JWT_TOKEN_HERE
Content-Type: application/json

### 16. Approve Task via Workflow System (replace TASK_ID with actual task ID)
POST http://localhost:8080/api/v1/approvals/TASK_ID/approve
Authorization: Bearer YOUR_JWT_TOKEN_HERE
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "signature": "test_digital_signature",
  "comment": "Approved via workflow system"
}

### 17. Reject Task via Workflow System (replace TASK_ID with actual task ID)
POST http://localhost:8080/api/v1/approvals/TASK_ID/reject
Authorization: Bearer YOUR_JWT_TOKEN_HERE
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "signature": "test_digital_signature",
  "reason": "Rejected via workflow system - insufficient justification"
}

### 18. Submit Requisition for Approval (creates workflow assignment and tasks)
POST http://localhost:8080/api/v1/requisitions/REQUISITION_ID/submit
Authorization: Bearer YOUR_JWT_TOKEN_HERE
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "comments": "Submitting for approval via workflow system"
}

### 19. Bulk Approve Multiple Tasks
POST http://localhost:8080/api/v1/approvals/bulk/approve
Authorization: Bearer YOUR_JWT_TOKEN_HERE
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "taskIds": ["TASK_ID_1", "TASK_ID_2"],
  "signature": "test_digital_signature",
  "comment": "Bulk approval via workflow system"
}

### 20. Bulk Reject Multiple Tasks
POST http://localhost:8080/api/v1/approvals/bulk/reject
Authorization: Bearer YOUR_JWT_TOKEN_HERE
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "taskIds": ["TASK_ID_1", "TASK_ID_2"],
  "signature": "test_digital_signature",
  "reason": "Bulk rejection via workflow system"
}

