### ❌ POST /api/v1/payment-vouchers/{id}/reject - Use workflow system instead
### ❌ POST /api/v1/grns/{id}/approve - Use workflow system instead
### ❌ POST /api/v1/grns/{id}/reject - Use workflow system instead

### WORKING ENDPOINTS SUMMARY:
### ✅ GET /api/v1/requisitions - List all requisitions
### ✅ GET /api/v1/requisitions/{id} - Get requisition by ID or REQ number
### ✅ GET /api/v1/documents/{id}/approval-status - Get approval status
### ✅ GET /api/v1/approvals/available-approvers - Get available approvers
### ✅ GET /api/v1/approvals - Get approval tasks
### ✅ POST /api/v1/approvals/{id}/approve - Approve via workflow system
### ✅ POST /api/v1/approvals/{id}/reject - Reject via workflow system
### ✅ POST /api/v1/requisitions/{id}/submit - Submit for approval (creates workflow)
### ✅ POST /api/v1/approvals/bulk/approve - Bulk approve tasks
### ✅ POST /api/v1/approvals/bulk/reject - Bulk reject tasks